f="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Nh%E1%BA%A5t-h%E1%BB%99c-ch%C3%A2u/poem-JNc_b8GQVyXk1IHrlg17mA">Nhất hộc châu - 一斛珠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Thanh-b%C3%ACnh-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-NB7nk8Nge4yBjrV5IbQvgA">Thanh bình điệu kỳ 3 - 清平調其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%B3-b%C3%A0-h%C3%A0nh/poem-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Tỳ bà hành - 琵琶行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Tri%E1%BB%87t/Y%C3%AAn-s%C6%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-6LE0W6_eEWWLua8-HFq7Ng">Yên sơn kỳ 1 - 燕山其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Tri%E1%BB%87t/author-fXc_gqkrGBbO64QEuTFarQ">Tô Triệt</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
